@@TPicState
Description:
This is the differents states for the state property of the TJvImage. 

* stDefault if displaying the default image (property Picture) 
* stEntered if displaying the entered image (property Pictures.PicEnter) 
* stClicked1 if displaying the clicked1 image (property Pictures.PicClicked1) 
* stClicked2 if displaying the clicked2 image (property Pictures.PicClicked2) 
* stDown if displaying the down image (property Pictures.PicDown)

